e hole. \nIn order to do so, you will be given two items in this game: a hammer and a heavy ball.\n\nJust putt the ball into the hole to complete each stage. \n-Try to avoid various terrain and obstacles.\n-Try using any method to complete the stage with the number of given opportunities.\n \n[Intuitive controls]\nPUTTZZLE is simple. Just putt the ball into the hole by any means. \n\n[Entertainment from simplicity]\nJust focus on putting the ball into the target.\nCalculate the number of cases to solve each stage. \n\n[Increasing difficulty level]\n[PUTTZLE] is like a puzzle. You will experience more complicated stages as you finish each stage with even more obstacles. \nYou can even utilize obstacles or avoid them to finish the stage.", "short_description": "PUTT YOUR BALL IN IT! "}]}, "developer_name": "Pixelity Gamelab", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://pixelitygames.com/privacy-policy/?lang=en", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://pixelitygames.com/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "Pixelity Games Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://pixelitygames.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS", "PUZZLE", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ko", "zh_CN", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1697321224016681"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "721355552939864"}]},